description:
MINIAURA POCKET-SIZE DIGITAL NIGHT-VISIO Product Details
Say goodbye to night vision devices with image intensifier tubes that burnout over time. The Mini Aura(TM) is a completely digital night vision monocular that won t burn out. The image seen will no longer be green but a crisp black and white view. The intensity can be easily adjusted with a simple push of a button. It boasts a 19-degree angle of view and you can see up to 82 feet in total darkness. The Mini Aura(TM) is compact and lightweight and can even fit in your pocket allowing you to bring it almost anywhere. Use the Mini Aura(TM) on camping trips for late night wildlife viewing, at dusk during hunting trips or during any outdoor activity. It can be used in ambient light or total darkness. The Mini Aura(TM) comes with a carry pouch and wristband. Uses 3 AAA batteries (not included
